full_summary:
[Title]
Rental and Support Services for Three (3) On/Off Road and Over Snow Personnel Transport Vehicles

[Description]
In support of Department of National Defence (DND) activities in the Canadian North, we are soliciting proposals for the rental of three (3) personnel transport vehicles (without operators) and associated services. The intention is to establish a single contract for a 10-month initial period, with two 1-year option periods. This notice actuates the procurement process for the acquisition of these services.

[Key Information]
* Estimated Quantity: 3 (three) vehicles
* Duration of Contract: 10 months (optionally extendable by up to 2 1-year periods)
* Time Frame of Delivery: Start date of December 1, 2024
* Security Requirement: None
* Work Location: Nunavut, Canada - Resolute Bay (Canadian Armed Forces Arctic Training Centre)

[Tender Closing Date and Time]
* Tender Closing Date: July 22, 2024 at 14:00:00 Eastern Daylight Time
* Corresponding Date: Monday, July 22, 2024

[Additional Information]
* Documents for this solicitation can be downloaded from the Canada Buys website.
* Bidders should refer to the tender documentation for complete details. 

[Attachment]
The complete solicitation documents are available here: [link]

# Target Audience
Government contractors, service providers with capabilities pertinent to this program.

**Notice Type**: Request for Proposal
**Procurement Category**: SRV
**Procurement Method**: Competitive - Open Bidding

**Regions of Opportunity**: World
**Regions of Delivery**: Canada, Nunavut Territory
Synergy proposal submissions must be made consistent to the guidelines stipulated for providers in the tender documentation.

**Languages Allowed**: English or French

You may request tenders in either English or French.

**Points of Contact**
Kayla Shabsove  
DND Acquisition Alliance  
(343) 596-9352  
kayla.shabsove@forces.gc.ca
